creator: tap4fun
descriptionHtml: In this game, you will establish your own territory, plan its layout, construct buildings, oversee production, gather resources, process a variety of materials, engage in trade, and recruit a variety of Hero partners—all in order to eventually establish a mighty trade route and conquer the world! Game Features: Heroes There are a variety of Heroes, each with unique skills. Some excel at leading troops in battle, others at cooking and building, still others excel at production and crafting—and you can recruit them all to assist the development of your territory! Production From raw logs to prepared lumber; from wood to furniture; from planting wheat to baking bread; from excavating ore to smelting metal; from weaving clothes to forging armor—it's all there for you to craft! Trade Gathering, producing, crafting, transporting, and trading! Whether from the village to the city or from the frozen tundra to the blistering desert—establish a mighty trade route and earn endless wealth! Kingdoms Do not fear being alone! Establish a mighty kingdom together with your friends, striving arm-in-arm for supremacy! On the journey of world domination, your kingdom will stand to support and defend you. You will trust each other with life and death, sharing in both honor and disgrace—all to conquer the world!
descriptionShort: Plan, build, produce, trade, and form an army to eventually conquer the world!

title: EMPIRE ISLAND

creator: Seagame
descriptionHtml:
***Group Hunts***
Danger looms in this prehistoric world where ferocious beasts roam. These giants cannot be defeated on your own - gather your friends and allies to hunt them down.

***Rebuild Your Home***
Start from the deserted island - Land of Revelations - and build your base, summon heroes, train troops, trade. Organize your base using various buildings, decorations, and more. It's up to you to decide how to customize your home.

***Find Clansmen***
Find lost members of your Clan. Gain their loyalty and they can help you increase your strength. Form an alliance with other players and join forces to fight against the Voidbringer, protect your allies from looters.

***Primitive Sacrifices***
Various tribal sacrifices will make you feel like you're in prehistoric times. Come and grow your Tribe with other members, worship Totems and Spirits, and receive divine rewards. Under the patronage of the Spirits, expand territory, enhance your strength and influence, and dominate the world.

***Trade and Commerce***
Resources are the key to development in this prehistoric world. Trade allows you to exchange resources you have for materials you need. Sell excess goods at a high price to get the Crystals you need to grow.

***Strategic Combat***
The long-awaited new version is finally here. Go to the Divine Hunting Ground to experience various combat modes and battle other champions. The Divine Hunting Ground is finally unveiled, come and play with friends from all over the world.

***Tribe vs. Voidbringer***
War rages between the righteous Tribesmen and the evil Voidbringers - there's no escape. You are a Chief in prehistoric time and the hope of the Clan. Establish your territory, design the layout, construct buildings, gather resources, produce goods, rear progeny, and trade with other Clans to grow your own Clan into a mighty power.
descriptionShort: Travel to super fun tribal ages with this casual strategy game

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- New "Chief" character with related progression and combat features. You can now control the Chief to fight in special maps!
- New features including Voidbringer Arena, Wonderrealm Adventures, Shrine Ruin challenges, trading with and rescuing villages, and more.
- New "soul wish" system and sacred "runes."
- New "order" function added to tribes, as well as many improvements to the interface and quests.
- Announcement, reply, and copy functions added to chat.
- Other optimizations and bug fixes.
